items.name: National Theatre Live: Of Mice and Men
items.text: Fathom Events, BY Experience and National Theatre Live invite you to John's Steinbeck revival Of Mice and Men, fresh off its record-breaking run on Broadway, in an extraordinary one-night cinema event on Thursday, November 6. Golden Globe® winner and Academy Award® nominee James Franco (127 Hours, Milk) and Tony Award® nominee Chris O'Dowd (Bridesmaids, Girls) star in the hit Broadway production Of Mice And Men, filmed on stage by National Theatre Live.  This landmark revival of Nobel Prize winner John Steinbeck's play is a powerful portrait of the American spirit and a heartbreaking testament to the bonds of friendship.
